import React from 'react'; const InfoTab = ({ match }) => { if (!match) return
Match info not available.
; const { localteam, visitorteam, venue, tosswon, elected, status, note, starting_at, type, league, stage, season, first_umpire, second_umpire, tv_umpire, referee, round, } = match; const formatDate = (dateStr) => { const date = new Date(dateStr); return date.toLocaleString(); }; const formatToss = (tossString) => { if (tossString === 'bowling') return 'bowl'; if (tossString === 'batting') return 'bat'; return tossString; // fallback if it's something else }; return (
Match {localteam?.name} vs {visitorteam?.name}
Status {status} {note && `- ${note}`}
Date & Time {formatDate(starting_at)}
Match Type {type?.toUpperCase()}
Match Round {round}
Toss {tosswon ? `${tosswon.name} elected to ${elected}` : ''}
League {league?.name}
Stage {stage?.name}
Season {season?.name}
Venue {venue?.name && `${venue.name}`}{venue?.city && `, ${venue.city}`} {venue?.capacity && `(Capacity: ${venue.capacity})`}
Umpires {first_umpire?.fullname && `${first_umpire.fullname} (On-Field)`} {second_umpire?.fullname && `, ${second_umpire.fullname} (On-Field)`} {tv_umpire?.fullname && `, ${tv_umpire.fullname} (TV)`}
); }; export default InfoTab;
